wiki.summary: “No Idea” serves as the lead single from Don Toliver’s debut studio album Heaven or Hell. On the track, Don reflects on a relationship with a girl who he truly likes and shows his intent to progress further. This track was heavily teased on Toliver’s Twitter account and most notably on Ninja’s stream with Travis Scott. It was officially announced on May 29th, 2019. Read more on Last.fm.
